♪ When I was trying to get to you ♪

01:21:10.699 --> 01:21:13.702
-[music ends]
-[audience applauding]

01:21:13.785 --> 01:21:15.620
And that audience loves it.

01:21:15.704 --> 01:21:17.581
And he's getting that thing

01:21:18.540 --> 01:21:21.668
that he loves,
that was the reason for all of it.

01:21:22.961 --> 01:21:25.505
It wasn't the money. Money is nice.

01:21:25.589 --> 01:21:29.926
It was 'cause that lights him up.
That's lit him up since he was a kid.

01:21:30.010 --> 01:21:32.012
[guitar riff playing]

01:21:35.765 --> 01:21:38.268
♪ The warden threw a party
In the county jail ♪

01:21:38.351 --> 01:21:40.896
