01:22:32.197 --> 01:22:35.283
or their disappointment
in the arc of his career,

01:22:35.367 --> 01:22:39.829
they say, "He didn't go where
his destiny was leading him enough."

01:22:39.913 --> 01:22:43.500
That night, he went
where his destiny was leading him.

01:22:43.583 --> 01:22:45.335
And he met it.

01:22:45.418 --> 01:22:47.295
♪ Dancing to the jailhouse rock ♪

01:22:47.379 --> 01:22:49.089
♪ We're dancing ♪

01:22:50.131 --> 01:22:52.342
♪ Yeah, we're dancing ♪

01:22:52.425 --> 01:22:55.261
♪ To the jailhouse rock ♪

01:22:55.762 --> 01:22:56.805
Ha!

01:22:57.722 --> 01:22:59.099
All right!

