01:24:11.880 --> 01:24:13.882
[heartfelt music playing]

01:24:14.632 --> 01:24:18.887
[O'Brien] All great show business stories
have to have

01:24:18.970 --> 01:24:20.513
more than one act.

01:24:21.681 --> 01:24:23.850
The real great ones have three acts.

01:24:26.102 --> 01:24:28.605
This special gives him a third act.

01:24:29.898 --> 01:24:31.691
And we all know where that ends,

01:24:32.442 --> 01:24:36.071
but at the beginning, it was pretty great.

01:24:40.116 --> 01:24:44.370
The thing I wish for Elvis Presley,
it's a weird thing to wish,

01:24:44.454 --> 01:24:46.998
but I wish people would have
some empathy for him.

01:24:51.294 --> 01:24:54.255
We turn celebrities into objects.

01:24:55.090 --> 01:24:56.299
This was a person.

01:24:57.342 --> 01:24:59.302
A person who was terrified,

01:24:59.928 --> 01:25:01.971
but putting it all out there.

01:25:02.055 --> 01:25:05.391
I'm joyous
when I see that special, because

01:25:06.267 --> 01:25:08.520
it's him standing up for himself.

01:25:14.692 --> 01:25:17.779
[slow guitar and horn tune playing]

01:25:28.706 --> 01:25:33.128
♪ There must be lights burning brighter ♪

01:25:33.211 --> 01:25:35.046
♪ Somewhere ♪

